<!--
	SU KIEN VAN TIEU
		- Config: Thiet lap tong quan
			- OpenTime: Thoi gian mo su kien
			- EndTime: Thoi gian dong su kien
			- DayOfWeek: Cac thu trong tuan dien ra su kien
			- MaxRoundsPerDay: So luot nhan tieu toi da trong ngay
		- Carriages: Danh sach xe tieu
			- Carriage: Thong tin xe tieu
				- Type: Loai xe tieu (0: Tieu thuong, 1: Tieu bach kim, 2: Tieu hoang kim)
				- Name: Ten xe tieu
				- ResID: ID Res (ID cua quai trong file Monsters.xml)
				- MoveSpeed: Toc do di chuyen
				- Vision: Tam nhin cua xe tieu. Khi xe tieu di chuyen, di den dau thi toan bo quai trong tam nhin se duoi theo de danh.
				- MaxHP: Sinh luc toi da
		- CargoNPCs: Danh sach NPC tiep tieu
			- NPC: Thong tin NPC
				- ID: ID NPC (xem o file NPCs.xml)
				- Name: Ten NPC
				- Title: Danh hieu
				- MapID: ID ban do
				- PosX: Toa do X
				- PosY: Toa do Y
		- Awards: Danh sach phan thuong van tieu
			- Award: Thong tin phan thuong
				- Type: Loai xe tieu
				- Money: Phan thuong bac
				- BoundMoney: Phan thuong bac khoa
				- Token: Phan thuong KNB
				- BoundToken: Phan thuong KNB khoa
				- Item: Thong tin vat pham thuong
					- ItemID: ID vat pham
					- Quantity: So luong
					- Bound: Khoa khi nhan khong
		- DeathPunishs: Danh sach vat pham roi ra khi tieu chet
			- Punishment: Thong tin roi
				- Type: Loai xe tieu
				- Drop: Thong tin vat pham roi
					- ItemID: ID vat pham
					- Quantity: So luong
					- Bound: Nhat len khoa hay khong
		- Paths: Danh sach duong di
			- Path: Thong tin doan duong
				- Type: Loai xe tieu
				- RequireLevel: Cap do yeu cau
				- RequireMoney: The chap bac
				- RequireBoundMoney: The chap bac khoa
				- RequireToken: The chap KNB
				- RequireBoundToken: The chap KNB khoa
				- LimitTime: Thoi gian van tieu toi da
				- MovePath: Thong tin ban do duong di
					- FromMapID: Tu ban do
					- ToMapID: Den ban do
			=> Di giua 2 ban do khac nhau hoac chung ban do, he thong se chon ngau nhien NPC nam trong ban do dich den de tra tieu
					
-->
